\title{{\bf Microscopic derivation of the Ginzburg-Landau equations for the periodic Anderson model in the coexistence phase of superconductivity and antiferromagnetism}}
\author{V.V. Val'kov, A.O. Zlotnikov\/\thanks{E-mail: zlotn@iph.krasn.ru}}
